title: Wheat Crop Acreage for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1917 (2)--Original Data, 1911-1937 (3)--Original Data, 1933-1944. Data Include The Saar Land. The Figure For 1935 Was Obtained By Adding The Average For The Saar Region To The Total Of Other Territory (See Statistiches Jahrbuch Fur Das Deutsche Reich, 1936, P. 40). Source: League Of Nations, Statistical Yearbook, 1939/1945, P. 90; International Institute Of Agriculture, International Yearbook Of Agricultural Statistics, 1941-42 To 1944-45, P. 4.

This NBER data series a01032c appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
